<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FEC7674F319E" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,367,375,400]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<heading id="40679246CE3E02056DD0FEC7674F319E" box="[132,367,375,400]" fontSize="10" level="2" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" reason="6">
<taxonomicName id="DC905EA9CE3E02056DD0FEC7674F319E" authority="Gory" authorityName="Gory" authorityYear="1841" box="[132,367,375,400]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aurocephalus">
<emphasis id="29E4F938CE3E02056DD0FEC7674F319E" bold="true" box="[132,367,375,400]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<emphasis id="29E4F938CE3E02056DD0FEC767113181" bold="true" box="[132,305,375,400]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. aurocephalus</emphasis>
Gory
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FE27678331A1" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,419,408,432]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Cor dorsal verde escuro.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="538A76A1CE3E02056DD0FE0767C4339E" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" type="description">
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FE0767BD31DE" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,413,440,464]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Fronte depressa, glabra.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FE67679631FE" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,438,469,496]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
— 
<specimenCount id="0D96EEA3CE3E02056DFEFE6A669E31FE" box="[170,190,469,496]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
cabeça vermelho-cobre.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FE476468321E" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,584,504,528]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Pronoto menos profundamente sulcado.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FDA764833221" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,675,536,560]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Estrias do pronoto mais superficiais e numerosas.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FD8767E4325E" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" box="[132,452,568,592]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Pubescência elitral amarela.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DD0FDE76412329E" blockId="4.[132,680,375,656]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">— Urosternito I sem protuberância, com mancha de pubescência lateral como os seguintes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B2F252ACE3E02056DE9FD0767C4339E" blockId="4.[132,681,696,912]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
Ficou-se muito tempo na indecisão se a espécie deveria ser descrita como subespécie endêmica da Mata Atlântica, como é o caso do 
<emphasis id="29E4F938CE3E02056CB2FD4766FD333E" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<taxonomicName id="DC905EA9CE3E02056CB2FD4766F8333E" authorityName="Curletti &amp; Migliore" authorityYear="2014" baseAuthorityName="Obenberger" baseAuthorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="chrysostictus" subSpecies="comizon">Agrilus chrysostictus comizon</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
mas a falta de dados corológicos relativos à 
<taxonomicName id="DC905EA9CE3E02056DD0FC876700335E" authorityName="Gory" authorityYear="1841" box="[132,288,824,848]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aurocephalus">
<emphasis id="29E4F938CE3E02056DD0FC876700335E" box="[132,288,824,848]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. aurocephalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
e as notávies diferenças morfológicas, principalmente na parte ventral, fizeram-nos optar para a separação a nível específico.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
